    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for Model Risk Level 2. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in the CPB application. Validation evidence demonstrates adequate predictive accuracy within combined uncertainty bounds across the full CPB operating envelope.",
